'''''Rack 'Em Up''''' is a [[Cue sports|Billiards/Pool]] [[arcade game]] developed by [[Konami]] in 1987 with two game types: 9-Ball or Rotation.

The Japanese title of the game is "The Hustler".<ref name="arcade-history.com">{{cite web |url=http://www.arcade-history.com/?n=rack-'em-up&page=detail&id=2150|title=Rack 'Em Up video game|work=arcade-history.com|accessdate=2010-07-22}}</ref>

